gh and far too complex but their purpose is an unfortunate nessecity in modern life. To 'opt' is to turn your back on your neighbor. <br /><br />Our derision of you is not founded on a secret admiration of your 'slacker' lifestyle but your lack responsibility to the society that provides you the safety to be a slacker. Is it remotely believable that you could maintain this lifestyle in most the other nations on the Earth? Do you believe for a moment that you will be able to take care of yourself 40 years from now with out any 401K or social security? You operate on platform of irresponsibility supported by a foundation of intellectually spurious theories.</span></font></td>
